room_title: Escape room "Alien Autopsy" by Escape In Time in Madison
room_description:
According to the US Government, this particular research facility was said to be abandoned in the 1950's... but you know better. Your old man made sure of that - It was his curiosity that cost him his life when he got too close to the truth.
According to the old man, the experiments being conducted here are enough to make your stomach turn inside out. Getting the exact coordinates wasn't easy, and the timeline is pretty tight. But, it's now or never... So take a deep breath. Get in. Get the proof. Get out alive!
